\pard \sl280 \tx360 \tx648 \tab \tab timing should be good to better than a second to keep the systematic error smaller than the likely random error in the midevent time determination\par 
\pard \sl280 \tx360 \tx648 \tx1080 \tab \tab \tab GPS good to better than a millisecond\par 
